author: Allan Smith
title: Tea party-style protests break out across the country against stay-at-home orders
description: The gatherings to oppose what critics say is gov't over-reach have been promoted by conservative commentators.
content:
Across the nation, protests against the stay-at-home orders health experts say are needed to save lives are taking place, with more set for the coming days.
This week, about 100 protesters gathered outside the Ohio statehouse in Columbus to push for Republic… [+5442 chars]
